Feature: Validate Amazon India upper navigation links # features/internal_links.feature:1
  As a user
  I want to verify the visible upper navigation links on Amazon.in
  So that I can ensure the navigation grid remains clickable and navigable
  Scenario: Validate the visible upper navigation links on Amazon.in    # features/internal_links.feature:6
    Given the user opens the Amazon India homepage                      # features/steps/internal_links_steps.py:9
    When the user collects the visible upper navigation links           # features/steps/internal_links_steps.py:16
    Then each visible link with a valid destination should be clickable # features/steps/internal_links_steps.py:22
    And each clicked link should navigate to a valid Amazon destination # features/steps/internal_links_steps.py:31
    And a screenshot should be captured for the navigation validation   # features/steps/internal_links_steps.py:43

